  },
  {
    title: '40+ Years Expertise',
    description: 'Deep specialization in Alfa Laval centrifuges. We understand every model, every application, every process variable.',
    icon: 'M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z',
  },
  {
    title: 'In-House Rebuild & Repair',
    description: 'Our Warren, MI facility rebuilds centrifuges to OEM specs with genuine Alfa Laval parts. Full testing before delivery.',
    icon: 'M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.066 2.573c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573 1.066c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066-2.573c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z',
  },
  {
    title: 'Pilot Testing Available',
    description: 'Send us your sample material. We test it in our lab with the right centrifuge and send you data-backed recommendations.',
    icon: 'M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4',
  },
